channel.title: [Released]Bandos Amulet, Armadyl, Saradomin & Zamorak[/Released]
channel.description:
[b]Do you like these amulet? i need to work some more on it, however here is a pic of the actuals, ;) :D[/b] download link here: [b][url=http://www.fileden.com/files/2008/8/1/2029618/God%20Amulet.rar]http://www.fileden.com/files/2008/8/1/2029618/God%20Amulet.rar [/url][/b] [b]Here The ints:[/b] [code] if(i == 13568) //Replace with the id you want { class8.aStringArray189 = new String[5]; class8.aStringArray189[1] = "Wield";//New option class8.anInt174 = 14050; //Model ID class8.anInt181 = 620; //620 zoom increase will make it smaller class8.anInt190 = 424; //424 model rotate up+down increase to move doen away from you class8.anInt198 = 8; //model rotate side ways increase to move right in circle class8.anInt169 = 1; // model offset increase to move to the right class8.anInt194 = 16; //model offset increase to move up class8.anInt165 = 14051;//male wearing class8.anInt200 = 14051;//female wearing class8.anInt175 = -1; class8.anInt197 = -1; class8.aBoolean176 = false;//Stackable class8.aString170 = "Bandos Amulet";//Name of the new item class8.aByteArray178 = "An ancient amulet used by the warriors of Bandos.".getBytes();//examin info } if(i == 13569) //Replace with the id you want { class8.aStringArray189 = new String[5]; class8.aStringArray189[1] = "Wield";//New option class8.anInt174 = 14052; //Model ID class8.anInt181 = 620; //620 zoom increase will make it smaller class8.anInt190 = 424; //424 model rotate up+down increase to move doen away from you class8.anInt198 = 8; //model rotate side ways increase to move right in circle class8.anInt169 = 1; // model offset increase to move to the right class8.anInt194 = 16; //model offset increase to move up class8.anInt165 = 14053;//male wearing class8.anInt200 = 14053;//female wearing class8.anInt175 = -1; class8.anInt197 = -1; class8.aBoolean176 = false;//Stackable class8.aString170 = "Armadyl Amulet";//Name of the new item class8.aByteArray178 = "An ancient amulet used by warriors of Armadyl.".getBytes();//examin info } if(i == 13570) //Replace with the id you want { class8.aStringArray189 = new String[5]; class8.aStringArray189[1] = "Wield";//New option class8.anInt174 = 14054; //Model ID class8.anInt181 = 620; //620 zoom increase will make it smaller class8.anInt190 = 424; //424 model rotate up+down increase to move doen away from you class8.anInt198 = 8; //model rotate side ways increase to move right in circle class8.anInt169 = 1; // model offset increase to move to the right class8.anInt194 = 16; //model offset increase to move up class8.anInt165 = 14055;//male wearing class8.anInt200 = 14055;//female wearing class8.anInt175 = -1; class8.anInt197 = -1; class8.aBoolean176 = false;//Stackable class8.aString170 = "Saradomin Amulet";//Name of the new item class8.aByteArray178 = "An ancient amulet used by the warriors of Saradomin.".getBytes();//examin info } if(i == 13571) //Replace with the id you want { class8.aStringArray189 = new String[5]; class8.aStringArray189[1] = "Wield";//New option class8.anInt174 = 14056; //Model ID class8.anInt181 = 620; //620 zoom increase will make it smaller class8.anInt190 = 424; //424 model rotate up+down increase to move doen away from you class8.anInt198 = 8; //model rotate side ways increase to move right in circle class8.anInt169 = 1; // model offset increase to move to the right class8.anInt194 = 16; //model offset increase to move up class8.anInt165 = 14057;//male wearing class8.anInt200 = 14057;//female wearing class8.anInt175 = -1; class8.anInt197 = -1; class8.aBoolean176 = false;//Stackable class8.aString170 = "Zamorak Amulet";//Name of the new item class8.aByteArray178 = "An ancient amulet used by the warriors of Zamorak.".getBytes();//examin info }[/code] [b]Sorry for not Gzipped but my DatMaker Cant load MQO Files and i don't know the reason :([/b] [b]Here is the info: First Extract "God amulet.zip" then open up bandos, search in inv & drop model folder theres a model if you want to edit neck, you can, convert it to .dat with DatMaker 1.3, don't forget to give the amulet emotion, do the same with the Bandos amulet wear, After you done with that use Gzip and Gzip them, don't forget to put it a number ID example like 14850 and 14851, Do the Same to all amulets. Put to the amulets exactly this ID So the ints will work if not ints will not work Bandos Wear 14050 Inv 14051
Amadyl Wear 14052 Inv 14053
Saradomin Wear 14054 Inv 14055
Zamorak Wear 14056 Inv 14057 Or Change all ints models number.
After you done put the ints into class8.java compile, Run Client say Add model 14050 Add model 14051 Add model 14052 Add model 14053 Add model 14054 Add model 14055 Add model 14056 Add model 14057 or Add models 14050 Add models 14051 Add models 14052 Add models 14053 Add models 14054 Add models 14055 Add models 14056 Add models 14057 close client compile, and you'll have the amulet configure other in the server so it wield in right spot and give bonuses[/b]
[b]Gods Amulets:[/b] [img]http://img160.imageshack.us/img160/3509/ammysslo8.png[/img]
[b]And thanks for reading, Bryan[/b]
Hope you every1 like these amulets and GL With it.
